thou not be co~tented to mocke vs
at home at thine owne house, but
art come to mock vs here, [$the one
tooke a waster, & dyd geue hym a
dosen stripes sayng,$] take this for
a reward, & mock vs no more.

[}THE XV. TALE.}]

   [$Theare was a yonge man of
Gotam the which should go
